Section 3: Roleplay / Personas

Example 3.1

User

You are a travel agent recommending a vacation destination.
AI Response

Based on what you've described — warm weather, culture, and great food — I'd strongly recommend
southern Italy. The Amalfi Coast is breathtaking, Naples has the best pizza in the world, and Pompeii offers
unforgettable history. Shall I start putting together an itinerary?

